    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s had some fun adventures, so there\u2019s a little bit of character here and there, but it runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next chapter. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
