    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing and rod bearing replacement. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis is tightened with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry remains precise. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains in peak operational form, offering the visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience enthusiasts crave.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
