    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin. I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home!",
