      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant, delivering 333 hp through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders, and the VANOS system has been professionally serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating common floor pan fatigue. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension, this vehicle offers the tactile feedback and telepathic turn-in characteristic of the marque's golden era. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, making it an ideal candidate for the spirited enthusiast.",
